ansible all --list --> to check all the hosts present in inventory
ansible playbook.yml --syntax-check  --> to check syntax of the playbook
ansbible playbook.yml -C  --> dry run without making any changes 
ansible-doc module-name   --> to check the documentation of the mentioned module
ansible-doc --list        --> to list all the available ansible modules
ansible all -m ping       --> to ping all the hosts present in inventory
ansbile-playbook playbook.yml --limit=servera  --> to limit a playbook to any particular instance 
